      "comment": "SUNSET CHROMIUM (2) settled off speed and overcame a collision with another runner to work home into the placings when second (22.49) at this track in a Free For All. Can find winning form here. ELITE DELUXE (3) has some solid form under her belt and proved too classy last time to win by 1.75 lengths at this track in a handy 22.37 beating SUNSET CHROMIUM. Likely to be in the finish. BOLT OF FUN (1) was strongly fancied last time but finished third (22.54), beaten 1.4 lengths. Goes well out of this box with a win and six minor placings. Can feature again. HURRY UP ERIC (7) bold run expected on best form.",
